UID:hBm33HYErKK0FVH4jgf37
SUMMARY:DJ 101: Intro to Digital Dejaying
DTSTAMP:20260327T072001Z
DTSTART:20260530T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Interested in learning more about DJ-ing? In this 3-hour crash 
	course\, students will learn the ins-and-outs of Serato\, playing and mixi
	ng tracks\, finessing your tracks\, and general tips and tricks for digita
	l Dejaying!\n\n*Use of a laptop is required to take part in this class — V
	era has a limited number of laptops available to borrow for membership. If
	 you need one to participate\, please email yewon.k@theveraproject.org to 
	confirm our availability.\n\nhttps://link.dice.fm/U5e17f1c6e22\n\nFrom The
